Key stakeholders will be available and engaged throughout the project lifecycle, providing necessary input and feedback during critical phases.

High-quality, structured data is available for training and fine-tuning the Gen AI models.
Historical support interaction data is accessible for model training.
The solution will comply with relevant data privacy regulations (e.g., GDPR, HIPAA).
Security protocols will be in place to protect sensitive data.
There will be a commitment to continuously monitor and improve the AI models based on user feedback and evolving needs.
Baseline data for comparison will be available to measure improvement.



Developing completely custom AI models from scratch is not part of the implementation; leveraging existing models and fine-tuning is the foc
Procurement of new hardware or infrastructure upgrades not related to Gen AI deployment is not included.
Guaranteeing specific performance outcomes (e.g., exact reduction in ticket resolution times) is not within the project's scope; instead, targets will be set as part of performance metrics.
